<div class="update-item">
    <img src="Images/BucketConnect/1.1.png" alt="Update Image 1" class="update-image">
    <div class="update-text">
        <h2>Castle Climbers 0.3</h2>
    </div>
    <button @onclick="() => ToggleDetails(0)" class="dropdown-arrow">
        @if (isOpen[0])
        {
            @:&#9650; <!-- Up Arrow -->
        }
        else
        {
            @:&#9662; <!-- Down Arrow -->
        }
    </button>

</div>

<div class="update-details">
    @if (isOpen[0])
    {
        <h3>Version 1.1.3</h3>
        <p>
            - Search bar implemented into ideas page <br />
            - Improved loading, downloading and deleting times <br />
            - Minor Bug Fixes
        </p>

        <h3>Version 1.1.2</h3>
        <p>
            - List view and photo view features added to lists <br />
            - Download counter for ideas fixed <br />
            - Limit of lists adjusted <br />
            - Major bug fixes
        </p>

        <h3>Version 1.1.1</h3>
        <p>
            - Added functionality to report issues <br />
            - Minor bug fixes
        </p>

        <h3>Version 1.1.0</h3>
        <p>
            - Navigation bar added to allow for quicker transitions between screens <br/>
            - Added the ability to create multiple lists, each with their own covers <br />
            - Added the ability to see progress on each list <br />
            - Added ideas function, allowing users to create, share and download user submitted lists <br />
            - Total progress can be seen in the account page <br />
            - Added achievements page <br />
            - Settings page added, providing functionality to view blocked users, view the privacy policy, logout of the account or delete the current account <br />
            - Minor bug fixes
        </p>
    }
</div>

<div class="update-item">
    <img src="Images/BucketConnect/1.0.png" alt="Update Image 1" class="update-image">
